We’d like to emphasize on the benefits of having a subscription vs one-time box  
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#e3fcef}
Acceptance criteria:

* Show a different copy in the free-addon banner if the user is part of any variation of the experiment
** Copy - Multi SKU: Subscribe and save – $XX OFF your first X boxes + FREE cut!
** Copy - Single SKU: Subscribe and save – $XX OFF your first X boxes + FREE {nameoffreecut}!
* Show a different copy in the discount banner if the user is part of any variation of the experiment
** Copy: Subscribe and save – $XX OFF your first X boxes!
* Remove the timer that shows x:xx minutes left in all banner variations

